==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incipient
<hw>In*cip"i*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>incipiens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>incipere</ets> to begin. See
<er>Inception</er>.]</ety> <def>Beginning to be, or to show itself;
commencing; initial; <as>as, the <ex>incipient</ex> stage of a fever;
<ex>incipient</ex> light of day.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>In*cip"i*ent*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

